            			<h4>OpenBSD</h4>            
								</div>
		</div></div><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-189-13-1" ><div class="panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-189-13-1-0">			<div class="textwidget"><p>
On OpenBSD, the Solarus engine is separated from the games (ZSDX and ZSXD). You do not have to install the engine separately; if you install one of the games and you do not already have the Solarus engine, it will be installed for you.
</p>
<p>
The Solarus engine and games are available from the ports collection: <strong>games/solarus</strong>.
</p></div>
		</div></div></div><div class="panel-grid" id="pg-189-14" ><div class="panel-grid-cell" id="pgc-189-14-0" ><div class="panel widget widget_circleicon-widget panel-first-child panel-last-child" id="panel-189-14-0-0">		<div class="circle-icon-box circle-icon-position-top circle-icon-hide-box circle-icon-size-small">
